annotation.TEXT: Oh, man. This Yoshi coin would be tricky to get without the green switch palace active.

Now, as for that Yoshi coin... Huh, no hidden blocks?
Oh, a springboard! Of course! That's how I would reach that previous Yoshi coin without flying!
All that's down here is more pollution and an ON/OFF switch that's probably important.

I'm surprised I dodged all that.
Double kill!

Wow, was I just not paying attention to that blatantly obvious nuclear waffle that was headed my way?
And this leads straight to Toxic House, surprisingly with no additional levels in between, even though it may have looked like there was plenty of room for more levels.

Patience. Don't be reckless when going for the reserve item!
